page.title: 10FAVOURITE FOODS
page.content: The favourite meal of people in tyhe area was English roast dinner.The second favourite was Chinese cookery, and then was fish and chips and salad. The least favourite was French cooking. The lunch most people liked was a snack. The second favourite was a cooked meal and the least favourite was a cold meal. In the evening the favourite meal was cooked dinner.The second favourite was high tea and the least favourite was late supper. The most popular breakfast was cereals, the second favourite was toast and the least favourite was English breakfast, which was a surprise.
